{"word":"κλωστήρ","slug":"κλωστήρ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κλωστήρ</b></el> <el>(κλωστήρ, ῆρος,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κλώθω'><el>κλώθω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a spindle</i>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a thread, yarn, line</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>λίνου κλ.</el> the flaxen <i>thread</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> the net, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}